==English==

===Noun===
'''Union Jack'''
# {{nautical}} {{American}} The flag, consisting of the blue star-studded [[field]] in the corner of the [[national ensign]], [[flown]] at the [[jack staff]] by ships at [[anchor]] (FM 55-501).
# {{nautical}} {{UK}} The flag, consisting of the flags of England, Scotland, and Ireland combined, flown on ships of the government of the United Kingdom
# The flag of the United Kindgom, consisting of the flags of England, Scotland, and Ireland combined.

[[Image:Flag of the United Kingdom.svg|thumb|250px|The Union jack of the United Kingdom.  [[Image:FIAV 111000.svg|20px]] Flag Ratio: 1:2]]

===Usage notes===
The '''Union Jack''' (also '''Union flag''', '''union jack''') is regarded as the official flag of the United Kingdom, although technically no law to that effect has ever been passed.